blasterhacks-2024.preview: I'm trying to maximize the amount of fun I have in college, so when I heard my friends were signing up for a hackathon, I knew I had to try. As a freshman, I wasn't really sure it would be for me, but it turned out to be a blast! Here's how it played out.
